sql:
SELECT total_savings
FROM savings_summary
WHERE service_id = 0;

external_knowledge:
- "blossoms are currently thriving" refers to services that are currently active and have active promotions;
- "substantial savings" refers to the highest total savings amounts;
- "top 10 services" means the results are limited to the top 10 based on total savings.

